- _ _ _ E _

- I cannot be at 1 ⇒ I must be at 2, 3, or 5.
- T cannot be at 3 ⇒ T must be at 1, 2, 4, or 5.  1 is R, 4 is E, so T must be at 2 or 5.

R _ _ E _

- V at 3 (new letter)
- E at 4 (fixed)
- T at 5 (allowed)

Therefore, the next logical guess is “RIVET”.
